The `Modal` component provides a focused dialog for user interactions, confirmations, or data entry. It supports various sizes, states, and customization options to create accessible and user-friendly modal experiences.

**Modal vs ComposedModal**

`Modal` is an all-in-one component configured through props, making it ideal for standard modal dialogs. For more complex layouts or fine-grained control, use [ComposedModal](/components/ComposedModal) instead.

